		{"id":"4b84dc6a6cfa828e","type":"text","text":"##### 🔎 Behind the scenes\nThis is an example of the rare case, that the linked webpage does not allow to be shown as an imbed. Evenly the content-page does not show the page. \nTherefor the html pages show the clickable url of the link as a heading which when clicked opens the linked page in new the browser-window.","x":2040,"y":-860,"width":360,"height":261,"color":"6"},
